---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { countries } from "../data/countries";
---

<Layout 
  title="Tax Calculator - Free Online Tax Estimator, Income Tax Calculator & Payroll Calculator | TaxPortal" 
  description="Use our free tax calculator for accurate income tax, payroll, capital gains, VAT, GST, stamp duty, and sales tax calculations. Estimate your tax refund, federal tax, state tax, and paycheck with our easy-to-use tax estimator tools for 10+ countries worldwide."
  image="https://personality.com/og-image.png"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-canvas-soft to-canvas dark:from-primary dark:to-primary" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl dark:text-on-primary">TaxPortal</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-body dark:text-muted">
          Your trusted source for tax calculators and international tax information. Whether you are filing your annual return, estimating quarterly tax payments, or comparing tax regimes, our tools help you understand and plan your taxes with confidence.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="/countries" class="rounded-pill bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-on-primary transition hover:opacity-90 dark:bg-on-primary dark:text-primary">Explore Countries</a>
          <a href="/blogs" class="rounded-pill border border-hairline px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-ink transition hover:border-primary dark:border-white/15 dark:text-on-primary">Read Tax Guides</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Featured Countries</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {countries.slice(0, 6).map(country => (
            <a href={`/countries/${country.slug}`} class="group rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 transition hover:border-primary hover:shadow-lg dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:hover:border-primary">
              <img src={country.flag} alt={`${country.name} flag`} class="h-16 w-auto mb-4 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-primary dark:text-on-primary">{country.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1 dark:text-muted">{country.continent}</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-body mt-3 line-clamp-3 dark:text-muted">{country.overview}</p>
              <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-link group-hover:underline dark:text-link">Explore taxes →</span>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline bg-canvas-soft dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-primary">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Popular Calculators</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {countries.slice(0, 6).flatMap(c => c.popularCalculators.map(pc => ({ ...pc, country: c }))).slice(0, 6).map(item => (
            <a href={`/countries/${item.country.slug}/${item.category}/${item.slug}`} class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 hover:border-primary transition dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:hover:border-primary">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <img src={item.country.flag} alt={item.country.name} class="h-8 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" />
                <span class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted">{item.country.name}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">{item.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1 dark:text-muted">{item.description}</p>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">All Countries</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5">
          {countries.map(country => (
            <a href={`/countries/${country.slug}`} class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 hover:border-primary transition dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary dark:hover:border-primary">
              <img src={country.flag} alt={`${country.name} flag`} class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-on-primary">{country.name}</span>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">How TaxPortal Helps You</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-3 dark:text-on-primary">Plan Your Taxes Confidently</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed dark:text-muted">Understand your tax obligations before they become surprises. Our calculators provide instant, accurate estimates using the latest tax brackets, rates, and rules for each country. Whether you are a salaried employee, freelancer, business owner, or investor, we have tools designed for your situation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-3 dark:text-on-primary">Compare Tax Regimes</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed dark:text-muted">Not sure which tax regime is best for you? Our comparison tools help you evaluate the old vs new tax regimes side by side, so you can make informed decisions about your tax strategy and maximize your take-home pay.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-3 dark:text-on-primary">Understand Your Deductions</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed dark:text-muted">From Section 80C investments in India to the standard deduction in the US, our guides and calculators help you identify every deduction and credit you may be eligible for. Don't leave money on the table.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas p-8 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-3 dark:text-on-primary">Stay compliant, stay informed</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed dark:text-muted">Tax laws change every year. We keep our calculators and guides updated with the latest rates, thresholds, and regulations so you can stay compliant and avoid penalties.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline bg-canvas-soft dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-primary">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">About TaxPortal</h2>
        <div class="prose max-w-none text-body dark:text-muted space-y-6">
          <p>TaxPortal is a free, comprehensive online platform dedicated to making international tax information accessible and actionable. We provide accurate tax calculators, detailed guides, and up-to-date tax rate information for individuals and businesses across multiple countries.</p>
          <p>Every calculator on our platform is built with precision, using official tax brackets, withholding tables, and statutory rates sourced from government authorities. Our content is reviewed by tax professionals to ensure accuracy and relevance.</p>
          <p>We believe that tax planning should not be a source of anxiety. By providing clear, well-structured tools and educational content, we empower users to take control of their financial future and make informed tax decisions.</p>
          <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> TaxPortal is for informational and educational purposes only. It does not constitute tax, legal, or financial advice. Always consult a qualified tax professional for advice specific to your situation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline bg-canvas-soft dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-primary">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">What is a tax calculator?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">A tax calculator is a tool that estimates your tax liability based on your income, deductions, filing status, and applicable tax rates. TaxPortal provides free, browser-based calculators for countries including the United States, India, the United Kingdom, Singapore, and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">How accurate are TaxPortal calculators?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">Our calculators use official tax brackets, rates, and rules from each country's tax authority. They provide accurate estimates based on the information you input. However, they are for informational purposes only and should not replace professional tax advice.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">Do I need to create an account to use the calculators?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">No. All TaxPortal calculators are completely free to use and do not require an account or personal information. All calculations are performed locally in your browser.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">How often are the tax rates updated?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">We update our calculators and guides as soon as new tax rates, brackets, or rules are announced by the relevant tax authorities. We strive to reflect the latest changes for every tax year.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">Can I compare old and new tax regimes?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">Yes. For countries that offer multiple tax regimes, such as India, our calculators allow you to compare both regimes side by side to determine which one minimizes your tax liability.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 dark:text-on-primary">Is TaxPortal free to use?</h3>
            <p class="text-body dark:text-muted">Yes, all basic calculators and educational content on TaxPortal are completely free. There are no hidden fees or subscription requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>